title: The Pleasure Cast - Complete Discog. June 2014 5 albums, 2 ep's
description:
Complete discography of UK aletrnative/Lo-fi Diy artist, The Pleasure Cast.
This guy has knocked out 5 albums and 2 Ep's in the last 2 years alone and over 20 more albums and EP's with other projects.
Mainman is Judas Vigilante. Check out his other projects which include Captain Kidder, Ark and Prudence Machete.
This discography is accurate and complete as of June 2014 and all files are labeleed correctly from my collection. Mp3's @ 320kbps. Covers incl. too.

Please seed and enjoy. This guy has had a very gard life and could do with you spreading the love. Plus he fucking hits the spot!
